# Configuration for the-welcome-bot - https://github.com/bash-bot/the-welcome-bot

# Message for a new user who open an issue
issueOpen: >
 Hello there!:wave: Welcome to our project!:gift_heart:
 Thankyou and congrats:tada:for opening your very first issue in this project.AnitaB.org is an inclusive community,committwd to creating a safe and positive environment:blossom:.
 Please adhere to our Code of Conduct:https://github.com/anitab-org/vms/blob/develop/code_of_conduct.md :raised_hands:
 You may submit a PR on the same if you like! If you want to report a bug:ladybug: please follow our bug_report.md template : https://github.com/anitab-org/mentorship-backend/blob/develop/.github/ISSUE_TEMPLATE/bug_report.md
 Also please make sure you include steps to reproduce it and be patient we will get back to you as soon as we can. :eyes:
 
 Also feel free to join us on Anita.org Open Source Zulip Community: https://anitab-org.zulipchat.com/#narrow/stream/223071-newcomers/topic/QA.20for.20Portal.20project.
 :handshake:  We have different streams for each active repo's for discussions.:silhouettes:Hope you have a great time here :).

